2. Decide on a galaxy layout.
3. Randomly determine player seating.
4. Randomly determine the first Speaker.
5. Choose factions.
6. Create the galaxy.
7. Gain starting units, technologies,
tokens, and other cards.
8. Randomly distribute 2 secret objectives
to each player, and each player chooses
1 to keep.
9. Reveal 2 stage I public objectives.

galaxy layout.

3. Each player places a tile, beginning
with the Speaker and going clockwise.
The order reverses each cycle; the last
player places 2 tiles in a row.

redistribute your command tokens.
6. Ready all cards.
7. Repair all units.
8. Return your strategy card.
